file.name: noOptional.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example API
paths:
  '/v1/resources/{resourceId}':
    get:
      operationId: getResource
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ResourceId'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Resource'
components:
  schemas:
    Resource:
      type: object
      properties:
        mandatoryInteger:
          type: integer
        mandatoryString:
          type: string
        mandatoryEnum:
          type: string
          enum:
            - 'one option'
            - 'another option'
        mandatoryDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
      required:
        - mandatoryInteger
        - mandatoryString
        - mandatoryEnum
        - mandatoryDate
  parameters:
    ResourceId:
      in: path
      description: Id of a resource.
      required: true
      name: resourceId
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
        minimum: 0
